{"tid":179280,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"消失的檔案首期眾籌成功","createTime":"2017-03-30T06:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T13:20:56.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35a2f6bf28ead00210d0e9e936c9116602906146","tid":179280,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:42:13.000Z","msg":"FringeBacker眾籌致謝場即將推出<br />\n<br />\n多得大家支持，《消失的檔案》FringeBacker眾籌捐款火速達到初步目標，說好了的眾籌捐款人致謝專場亦已備妥。兩場致謝專場將分別安排在4月中及5月初，港島區及九龍區各一場，以供選擇。導演羅恩惠將親臨致謝，分享《消失的檔案》攝製經歷及心路歷程。<br />\n<br />\n我們將以電郵通知各捐款人，選擇場次，若時間未能配合，各位可選擇保留權利，參與下一輪的致謝專場。<br />\n<br />\nFringeBacker眾籌平台暫時只向我們提供早期的279位捐款人電郵，在3月20日17:33後的捐款人電郵，要在眾籌到達30萬目標或5月15日後才會收到。因此，我們將會安排第二輪捐款人致謝場，日期及地點容後公佈。<br />\n<br />\n向30萬進發。<br />\n【支持眾籌 目標30萬】請前往FringeBacker 網頁 <a href=\"https://goo.gl/xZHzTF \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FxZHzTF%20&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3NtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a3fa62e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/xZHzTF </a><br />\n<br />\n************<br />\n#消失的檔案眾籌 #六七暴動 #反英抗暴 #羅恩惠 #香港1967<br />\n消失的檔案網頁﹕<a href=\"http://vanishedarchives.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvanishedarchives.org&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3NtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=002ab09b\" target=\"_blank\">vanishedarchives.org</a>"},{"pid":"d1682b4aa6e0c43526c0ea833d3d1f40e476e391","tid":179280,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:42:59.000Z","msg":"佢個網站冇捐都有得book去睇，$70一場，但勁full"},{"pid":"b6e23a609c6ee9af4d0b8f12df97c7df2ab9cee5","tid":179280,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T13:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正野"}]}